  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 7th level, your hunting instinct has grown tremendously, you gain 15 feet of blindsight. Additionally, while your Kagune is active, your sclera turns pitch black, as your irises and pupils turn red manifesting what is known as a Kakugan. For the duration of your Kakugan, your blindsight range doubles, and you gain advantage on Perception checks and Survival checks to track a creature.</p><p data-start=\"518\" data-end=\"759\">Starting at 11th level, you can activate your Kakugan for 1 minute as a Bonus Action by spending 2 RC Cells without needing to have your Kagune active. At 15th level, your blindsight range increases to 30 feet, and at 18th becomes 60 feet.</p>",
